item.title: Nike Yoga Dri-FIT
item.dc:creator: binh002tn
item.description: Move with ease in 360 degrees of comfort and support in these high-waisted leggings. Soft, sweat-wicking fabric stretches with you effortlessly while you flow through your poses. Colour-blocked panelling and curved seam lines follow your shape for a sleek look as you bend and reach. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.
